org.nats

Class Server

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nats.Server

  • public class Server
extends Object
    Server holds a list of Nats server and attributes returned from "INFO" operation. "next" method rotates server list for failover.
    Author:
    Teppei Yagihashi
